द्वौ भूतसर्गौ लोकेऽस्मिन् दैव आसुर एव च।
दैवो विस्तरशः प्रोक्त आसुरं पार्थ मे श्रृणु।।     -6-

द्वौ - two; भूतसर्गौ - type of beings; लोके - in the world; अस्मिन् - exists; 
दैव आसुर एव श्रृणु - divine and demon; दैवः - divine; विस्तरशः - at length; प्रोक्तः - has been described;
आसुरं - demon; पार्थ - O partha; मे श्रृणु - listen from me;

There are two types of beings in this world, O partha, the one possessing a divine nature and other possessing 
a demonic nature. Of these, former has been dealt at length, now hear in details from me the later one.


